Welcome to Natural Gas IntelligenceDear Mathew Thank you for your interest in receiving a free trial to Natural Gas Intelligence the industrys leading news and pricing service since You have a trial subscription to NGIs Daily Gas Price Index NGIs Weekly Gas Price Index Natural Gas Intelligence the Weekly Newsletter NGIs Bidweek Survey You will need to use your username and password to access the website Username msmith Password dq Keep in mind that both the username and password are case sensitive meaning that username johnsmith is not the same as JohnSmith Your trial is active until Your trial subscription offers you access to three publications Here is a brief overview of each Daily Gas Price Index includes The latest breaking industry news in a concise easytoread format Cash and NYMEX prices with market analysis Weekly Gas Price Index is updated each Monday and includes NGIs first of the month Bidweek Price Survey Futures and Weather Data Natural Gas Intelligence is updated each Monday and includes Impact of electric industry restructuring and the emerging power markets Supplydemand changes and projections And dont forget you will also be able to Create customized cash and futures pricing graphs Graph current storage levels against historical figures Search our comprehensive news archive to find the story you need If you have any questions about other products or services we offer call tollfree or email Your account is now active Please visit Cathleen H Behan Marketing Sales Director Intelligence Press Inc PS Want to subscribe today Call now and we will give you four weeks free ALL RIGHTS RESERVED c Intelligence Press Inc
